	For other Yahoo coverage, see Yahoo.xml.

	Different content HTTP/HTTPS:
		amt.flickr.com
		auto-up.flickr.com
		bup.flickr.com
		up.flickr.com

	Invalid certificate:
		rw.api.flickr.com
		hv-static.flickr.com
		\d.hv-static.flickr.com
		images.flickr.com (broken chain)
		photos\d.flickr.com
